  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nA simple `const blockRootsAtSlot = new Map<phase0.Slot, phase0.Root>();` at https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/e04410b5704f04738c03a75673efff6b829f1700/packages/beacon-state-transition/src/phase0/epoch/processPendingAttestations.ts#L29\r\n\r\nhelps save ~0.5s per epoch transition in the performance test (~2.1s in total).\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nCache blockRoots in CachedBeaconState similar to `validators, balances` so that we don't have to go to persistent-merkle-tree to get data, this should help speed up the whole state transition instead of just `processPendingAttestations` in phase0.",
