    "body": "to be clear, the performance test `slots.test.ts` was not stable enough, the difference from caching `blockRoots` in epoch transition is only 100ms-150ms, not 500ms.\r\n\r\nand if I cache block roots using `persistent-ts` in CachedBeaconState, the sync time is even slower probably because of the cost of mutating `persistent-ts` leaf (it has to allocate a new array of 32 blockRoots)",
