    "body": "This is a profile from a Prater sync, `getBlockRootAtSlot` takes 4% of the time\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1290\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-07-14 at 10 53 19\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/125558567-77575c36-66d7-491d-97c6-e0b4e868809d.png\">\r\n\r\nEach epoch has 32 * 128 attestations, we really only need to get block roots at 32 slots instead of `32 * 128 = 4096`.\r\nWe should apply the cache strategy for both phase0 and altair. \r\n",
